y":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:40:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上網搵過CCCU PAM同 HKCC SPA嘅升學率。<br />\nPam嘅ugc 升學率高過 Spa 10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我最後揀左CCCU PAM<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：都係DSE考得差想入返政政<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同學加油 到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fc5524d8d3d9bef0665552f72a14f8017935f1","tid":322373,"uid":122551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T02:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你有哂2邊offer？</blockquote><br />\n係呀。"},{"pid":"979453e9ea9b9a28db0738e6dbf7c8442f2dc7dc","tid":322373,"uid":46219,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:33:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打你有哂2邊offer？</blockquote><br />\n係呀。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有兩邊offer，結果揀咗PAM<br />\n一 課程設計吸引 有必修嘅summer intern，fyp係以影片提交<br />\n二 PAM嘅mentor好樂意幫freshmen 呢幾日解答咗我唔少問題<br />\n三 cccu賣盤消息令好多人湧去hkcc 我擔心hkcc會超收學生 到時資源會被分薄"},{"pid":"9bd5feb387c25c60ab31fab372cd864af95a5bde","tid":322373,"uid":80924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上網搵過CCCU PAM同 HKCC SPA嘅升學率。<br />\nPam嘅ugc 升學率高過 Spa 10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我最後揀左CCCU PAM<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：都係DSE考得差想入返政政<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊度可以搵到hkcc spa升學率？"},{"pid":"57537d7c13f62e1b2d96b1e8650b700222b9bf0f","tid":322373,"uid":122551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T06:02:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e5c6eca5928111fe3e818c53ee5b8ebc16bd473","tid":322373,"uid":46219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T06:48:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我上網搵過CCCU PAM同 HKCC SPA嘅升學率。<br />\nPam嘅ugc 升學率高過 Spa 10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我最後揀左CCCU PAM<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：都係DSE考得差想入返政政<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊度可以搵到hkcc spa升學率？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應用社會科學副學士(社會政策及行政)課程畢業生的升學率在過去三年（2014至2016年）一直攀升，由2014年的80.6%，上升至2015年的89.1%及2016年的96%，當中升讀八大院校政府資助學士學位課程(UGC-funded)的數字同樣錄得顯著升幅，由2014年的35%升至2015年的51.1%及2016年的57.1%。<br />\n<br />\n同學升讀八大的政府資助高年級學士學位課程（Senior Year Place）以理工大學的社會政策及行政(榮譽)文學士課程及城市大學的公共政策及政治社會科學學士課程為主；此外，亦有同學進入中文大學修讀政治與行政學或全球研究。<br />\n<br />\nHkcc send嚟嘅email係咁講。<em></em>"},{"pid":"401077b1c5d623f2426adb1ee7b9ff7fec16c8ac","tid":322373,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打你有哂2邊offer？</blockquote><br />\n係呀。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有兩邊offer，結果揀咗PAM<br />\n一 課程設計吸引 有必修嘅summer intern，fyp係以影片提交<br />\n二 PAM嘅mentor好樂意幫freshmen 呢幾日解答咗我唔少問題<br />\n三 cccu賣盤消息令好多人湧去hkcc 我擔心hkcc會超收學生 到時資源會被分薄</blockquote><br />\n識自己做分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58aabe8a181217de002d3d47db99d8034ff337d","tid":322373,"uid":68026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:46:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上網搵過CCCU PAM同 HKCC SPA嘅升學率。<br />\nPam嘅ugc 升學率高過 Spa 10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我最後揀左CCCU PAM<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：都係DSE考得差想入返政政<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我係咪見過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記住得閒17號前可以返黎Join我地個Camp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n包你開學順順利利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91feaaef3fc3c0beeedac60218e078c7e289308c","tid":322373,"uid":43983,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:51:20.000Z","msg":"垃圾科<br />\n利申：SPA graduate"}]}